<h2 class="bold font-l">Sasuke tries to be a good dad</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Emphasis on &quot;tries&quot;. Due to a good chunk of his life being directed by vengeance, Sasuke has no social skills whatsoever. And it shows when he tries to spend time with his daughter Sarada during Parent and Child Day. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/AmazinglyEmbarrassingParents" class='trope-example-link'>Amazingly Embarrassing Parents</a></p>
</div>
